Robert Durst appeared in court on Tuesday and pleaded not guilty to a new charge of possessing a gun after a felony conviction . 
  The millionaire was arrested last month on suspicion of the 2000 murder of his friend Susan Berman . 
  He also faces a murder charge in California and two state weapons charges in Louisiana . 
  Durst pleaded guilty to two federal charges in Pennsylvania in 2004 . 
  He is accused of killing Berman because she was about to testify about the 1982 disappearance of his first wife . 
  He faces a trial date of June 22 . 
 